locality: Ca. 14 Km ESE of Vigia; Campina do São Benedito. Savanna woodland or open, treeless Lagenocarpus savanna with adjoining gallery forest. Edge of shrubby secondary growth through white-sand savanna.

Reserva Florestal de Corotire (Kayapó-Indian-Reservation). Surroundings of Gorotire village at Rio Fresco. Landscape with hills and mountains up to ca. 500 m. alt. General vegetation consists of nonflooded and flooded primary and secondary forest, cerradão, cerrado, campo cerrado, as also plantations and abandoned fields. This stand: 3 km downstream of village. Forest flooded at least one month per year (March). Collected along trail crossing various ecozones
